    "description": "Strike gold wherever adventure takes you!<br><br>This ASR Outdoor gold panning kit is lightweight and easily portable, meaning you walk or hike to just about any river or creek with gold prospecting equipment on your back, and immediately start panning for gold; minimal set up time needed and no assembly required.<br><br>All gold prospecting equipment included in this gold panning kit, conveniently fit inside the included ASR Outdoor drawstring backpack, so you can remain hands free when you’re on the go, and easily pack everything out when you’re done for the day.<br><br>Designed for use right at the water’s edge, this kit includes a high quality 12 inch dual riffle gold pan that makes capturing gold easier with both shallow and deep riffle walls. The gold panning kit also comes with three essential mini stacking classifiers, to help increase gold recovery efforts by eliminating unwanted raw materials from your paydirt. The included scoop is perfect for digging into creeks and streams, while the fine gold recovery equipment helps in the collection of even the smallest gold flakes and flour.<br><br>Lastly, this gold panning kit also includes a compatible stacking classifier storage container to catch paydirt, or securely store any other found valuables like rocks or fossils while exploring in the wild.<br><br>Adventure awaits; good luck!",
